---
title: Balsamic & Fig Beef Tenderloin plus Honey Walnut Crostini
description: Whether you’re celebrating with a special someone or the whole gang, this two-course stunner will help take the stress out of the holidays. You’ll start with savory crostini topped with whipped ricotta, honey, and walnuts. And for the main, fig jam is paired with balsamic vinegar to create a tangy pan sauce to drizzle over tender beef tenderloin. Garlicky mashed potatoes and caramelized Brussels sprouts are the perfect accompaniments. This holiday season, spend a little less time in the kitchen and more time enjoying the season.
